<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fb923c, #f97316);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #fb923c;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .order-info {
      background: #f0f9ff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🍪 We'd Love Your Feedback!</h1>
    <p>Help us bake even better cookies</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>Hi <%= @customer_name %>!</h2>
    
    <p>Thank you for choosing Mang Crinkle! We hope you absolutely loved your delicious crinkle cookies.</p>
    
    <% if @order %>
      <div class="order-info">
        <h3>Your Order Details:</h3>
        <p><strong>Order #:</strong> <%= @order.id %></p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
        <p><strong>Total:</strong> $<%= number_with_precision(@order.total_price, precision: 2) %></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    
    <p>Your experience matters to us! Would you take a moment to share your thoughts? Your review helps other cookie lovers discover our treats and helps us continue improving.</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="<%= @review_url %>" class="cta-button">Write Your Review</a>
    </div>
    
    <p><strong>Why your review matters:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>🌟 Help other customers discover amazing cookies</li>
      <li>💝 Support our small family business</li>
      <li>🚀 Help us improve and grow</li>
      <li>👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Share the joy of Filipino treats</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>It only takes a minute, and your honest feedback is incredibly valuable to us.</p>
    
    <p>Salamat (thank you)!<br>
    The Mang Crinkle Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This review invitation expires in 30 days.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at info@mangcrinkle.com</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 